 anting.  All you need to do is simply show up and Friends of Trees will pro
 vide coffee and breakfast treats\, gloves\, tools and guidance from trained
  crew leaders.  Just dress appropriately for the weather and wear sturdy wo
 rk shoes.  If you have any questions\, please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@F
 riendsofTrees.org or 503-282-8846 x24. 
