DESCRIPTION:<p><b>=========</b></p><p><b>Due to popular interest\, this eve
 nt is <u>full and closed</u></b>. We hope to work with you at another event
  of your choice!</p><p><b>========<wbr />=</b></p><p><b>Let's plant trees t
 ogether in NE Salem! </b>Interested in receiving a tree? Click <a href="htt
 ps://friendsoftrees.org/get-a-tree/"><u><u><u><u><b><u>HERE</u></b></u></u>
 </u></u></a> to purchase a tree for your household. Dozens of large (6-10' 
 tall) trees will be ready for planting in their new homes\, and your help i
 s what makes this community planting possible!</p><p>Please arrive by 8:45a
 m to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 9:00am
 . We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, as well as light breakfast sna
 cks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate. We ask that all volunteers dress for the 
 weather\, wear sturdy shoes/boots you don't mind getting dirty\, and be rea
 dy to have fun!</p><p><b>Have a pickup truck?</b> We need your help getting
  these young trees to their planting sites a few blocks away from the centr
 al staging site. <b><a href="https://www.tfaforms.com/4840511?tfa_26=a0T5G0
 0000fQk9Y&tfa_2189=NE%20Salem%20neigborhood%20planting&tfa_31=a0V5G00000W2c
