DESCRIPTION:Neighbors will plant trees in their neighborhood. Click on "Ord
 er Street & Yard Trees" to set up an account to buy trees for your yard or 
 parking strip.\n\nOnce you set up an account\, Friends of Trees will arrang
 e for the city of Portland to inspect the planting site and issue a permit.
  For this planting\, you must create your account by Nov 10 and order your 
 trees by Dec 15.\n\nQuestions? Contact your Neighborhood Coordinator.\n\nCr
 eston-Kenilworth: Kate\, 503-236-7954 or kate@constantrider.com.\n\nEastmor
 eland: Susan\, 503-703 or emtreeplanting@gmail.com\, or Philip\, 503-777-27
 58 or PhilipJanel@msn.com.\n\nReed: Carol & Rob\, 503-284-7260 or trees@ree
 dneighborhood.org.\n\nWoodstock: Julie\, 503-774-7441 or woodstocktrees@gma
 il.com.\n\n\n
