 our started. We'll also provide gloves\, tools\, and tree planting guidance
 \, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing stu
 rdy shoes and we'll assign you to a planting team led by one of our trained
  Crew Leaders. \n\nRSVPs are not required. Please contact Andy or Jenny at 
 (503) 595-0213 for more information.  We look forward to seeing you out the
 re! 
