DESCRIPTION:Volunteer to help grow greener neighborhoods by joining a Frien
 ds of Trees staff member in calling our âtreecipientsâ to help them pic
 k out new trees for their homes and streets. Youâll learn about the diffe
 rent types of trees available through FOT planting programs\, and how to he
 lp neighbors navigate the FOT website and tree ordering process.\n\nThis ro
 le directly contributes to our ability to plant more trees in neighborhoods
 . A short training is required -- and youâll be asked to commit to at lea
 st three Wednesday evenings at our office at 3117 NE MLK Blvd in NE Portlan
 d.\n\nEmail our Volunteer & Outreach team at volunteer@friendsoftrees.org t
 o join in!
