DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer -- or click <a href= h
 ttps://friendsoftrees.org/plant-it-programs>HERE</a> to purchase a tree for
  your home.\n\nPlease arrive to the staging site\, The Lumberyard\, by 8:45
 am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting starts prom
 ptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show
  up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighborhood vol
 unteers will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the plan
 ting is complete.\n\n<b>Looking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kind
 ly requested for groups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://www.fr
 iendsoftrees.org/volunteering/group-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs a
 re not required for groups of 4 or less.\n\nPlease contact Jenny & Randi at
  (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more information.\n\nWe l
 ook forward to seeing you out there!\n\n<i>This event is generously sponsor
 ed by <b>J. Frank Schmidt & Son Co</b> and <b>Orchard Supply Hardware</b>.<
 /I>\n\n
