DESCRIPTION:Join Friends of Trees to plant street and yard trees in SE Port
 land! Pre-registration has closed at this point\, but feel free to show up 
 on Saturday and sign our waivers on-site. Thank you for choosing to make su
 ch a positive impact in your community!<br><br>Dozens of large (6-10â tal
 l) trees will be ready for planting in their new homes across these neighbo
 rhoods\, <u>and your help is what makes this community planting possible!</
 u><br><br>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and enjoy some breakfast treat
 s and coffee\, tea\, or hot chocolate. The planting starts promptly at 9:00
 am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, so all you need to do is sho
 w up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots â and be r
 eady to have fun!&nbsp\; Our neighborhood volunteers with also provide a po
 tluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete.<br>&nbsp\;<b
 r><b>Have a pickup truck? </b>We need your help getting these young trees t
 o their planting sites a few blocks away from the central staging site. Ple
 ase sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/truck" target="_blank
 ">www.friendsoftrees.org/truck</a> if you're able to help us out in this ke
 y role.&nbsp\;<br><br><b>This event will have a bike planting crew!</b> Wan
 t to join the bike team? Sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/
 bike" target="_blank">www.friendsoftrees.org/bike</a>. Bikers with trailers
  and cargo bikes are awesome\, but anyone with a bike is welcome to take pa
 rt!&nbsp\;<br><br><b>Under age 18?</b> A signed <a href="http://friendsoftr
 ees.org/images/stories/pdf/Youth_Waiver_2015.pdf" target="_blank">youth wai
 ver</a> is required for you to volunteer. We ask that youth 15 years and yo
 unger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny\, Pablo\, an
 d Carey at 503-595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" ta
 rget="_blank">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a>&nbsp\;if you have questions 
 or need any further information. We look forward to seeing you out there!<b
 r><br>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsor\, <a href="https://dossierhotel
 .com/" target="_blank">Dossier</a>!<br>===&nbsp\; &nbsp\;
