DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\
 nTo find your tree\, click <a href= https://friendsoftrees.org/plant-it-pro
 grams>HERE</a> to get started!  Be sure to start this process by <b>12/23/1
 3.</b>\n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast tr
 eats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\
 , so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing stur
 dy shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch fo
 r all volunteers after the planting is complete.\n\nRSVPs are kindly reques
 ted for groups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://www.friendsoftr
 ees.org/volunteer/group-registration-request-form>HERE</a> to do so.   Plea
 se contact Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or nee
 d more information. \n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!\n
