DESCRIPTION:<br><b><p></p><hr>========</b><br><b><br></b><br><b><u>Thank yo
 u for your interest\, this training is now full.</u></b>&nbsp\; If you're i
 nterested in being contacted when our next Crew Leader training opportunity
  arise\, please shoot us an email: volunteer@friendsoftrees.org&nbsp\; We m
 ay hold a Winter online training\, and with certainty this training will ha
 ppen again in Fall 2021.<br><b><br></b><br><b>========</b><br><br><a href="
 https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer/how-to-volunteer/crew-leader/" id="ow5
 677" __is_owner="true">Planting C</a><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/vo
 lunteer/how-to-volunteer/crew-leader/" __is_owner="true">rew Leaders</a>&nb
 sp\;are trained volunteers who are crucial to planting trees properly at mo
 re than 25 planting events this coming planting season. Friends of Trees is
  aiming to plant more than 3\,000 street and yard trees in our Neighborhood
  Trees Program\, and we can't do it without your help.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<br><b>
 <p></p></b><ul><li><b><u>What about Covid-19?</u></b>&nbsp\;We are requirin
 g all volunteers and staff to wear fabric face masks at our events\, and ke
 ep 6' or more of physical space from folks outside of your household.&nbsp\
 ; After the training at our planting events\, you will be planting with one
  other experienced Crew Leader or staff member.&nbsp\; We'll explain more a
 t the training\, but also feel free to check out our <a href="https://frien
 dsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">Covid-19 &amp\; Volunteer FAQ page</a>.&nbsp\
 ;</li></ul><ul><li><b><u>A note on planting location and personal transport
 ation</u>:</b>&nbsp\;You will be eligible to Crew Lead at plantings in the 
 following cities: Vancouver\, Portland (N\, NE\, SE\, E)\, Gresham\, Milwau
 kie\, Oregon City\, and Wilsonville.  Due to Covid-19\, personal transporta
 tion is necessary -- we're sorry that we will not be encouraging carpooling
  to planting sites this season.</li></ul><b><p></p><hr><p></p></b>Ple<u></u
 >ase contact Jenny or Pablo if you need more information or have questions:
 &nbsp\;<a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org">volunteer@frien<u></u>
 dsoftrees.org</a>. We look forward to working with you this planting season
 !
