DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\
 nPlease meet us in the A-Frame building in the NE corner of campus.  \n\n**
 The best entrance is on NE 87th\, 1/2 block east of NE Glisan.**\n\nPlease 
 arrive by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The planti
 ng starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you need
  to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our ne
 ighborhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers 
 after the planting is complete. This planting sponsored in part by the gene
 rous support of Portland General Electric.\n\nRSVPs are not required. Pleas
 e contact Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need
  more information. We look forward to seeing you out there!
