DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\
 nTo find your tree\, click <a href= https://friendsoftrees.org/plant-it-pro
 grams>HERE</a> to get started!  Be sure to start this process by <b>12/9/13
 .</b>\n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast tre
 ats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\,
  so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturd
 y shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for
  all volunteers after the planting is complete.\n\nRSVPs are kindly request
 ed for groups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://www.friendsoftre
 es.org/volunteer/group-registration-request-form>HERE</a> to do so.   Pleas
 e contact Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need
  more information. \n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!\n
