DESCRIPTION:<p>========</p><p><span>Due to the current snowy/icy conditions
 \, our tree nursery deliveries have been postponed due to potentially hazar
 dous roads. Unfortunately\, this means the </span><b><u>D Street Park plant
 ing event is postponed until Sat\, April 12th</u></b><span>.  If you are in
 terested in participating\, please sign up!  Thank you for your patience an
 d understanding with this change of plans.</span></p><p><span>========</spa
 n></p><p><span>Let's plant trees together at D Street Park! Dozens of large
  (6-10' tall) trees will be ready for planting in their new homes\, and you
 r help is what makes this community planting possible!</span></p><p>Please 
 arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting s
 tarts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, as well as ligh
 t breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate. We ask that all volunteers
  dress for the weather\, wear sturdy shoes/boots you don't mind getting dir
 ty\, and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request that y
 outh 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can
  volunteer on their own and will need to hand us a <b><u><a href="http://fr
 iendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u
 ></u></u></a></u></b> signed by their parent/guardian.</p><p><b>Questions? 
  </b>Please check out our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunte
 er-faq/" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u>
 </u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  You c
 an reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" ta
 rget="_blank"><u><u><b><u><u><u><u><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></u><
 /u></u></u></b></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213. We look forward to planting tog
 ether soon!</p><p>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsors <a href="https://p
 ortlandgeneral.com/" target="_blank"><u><u><u>Portland General Electric</u>
 </u></u></a>.</p><p>===</p><b><hr /></b><p>This event is in partnership wit
 h the City of Salem.</p>
