 of large (6-10' tall) trees will be ready for planting in their new homes\,
  and your help is what makes this community planting possible!</p><p>Please
  arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting 
 starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, as well as lig
 ht breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate. We ask that all volunteer
 s dress for the weather\, wear sturdy shoes/boots you don't mind getting di
 rty\, and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Have a pickup truck?</b> We need y
 our help getting these young trees to their planting sites a few blocks awa
 y from the central staging site. <b><a href="https://www.tfaforms.com/48405
 11?tfa_26=a0TPa00000qajae&tfa_2189=East%20Portland%2DNorth%20neighborhood%2
