 ></u></u></u></u></u></a> / 503-595-0213 We look forward to working togethe
 r soon!<br></p><p><b>What neighborhoods will the trees be planted in?</b> A
 rgay Terrace\, Hazelwood\, Parkrose\, Parkrose Heights\, Russell\, and Wilk
 es.</p><p>Thank you to our event sponsors <a href="https://www.nba.com/blaz
 ers/" target="_blank"><u>Portland Trail Blazers</u></a> and <a href="https:
