DESCRIPTION:Join our popular group of key volunteers! Sign up for our free 
 training to learn how to lead volunteer planters at morning tree plantings.
  As a trained crew leader\, you'll guide a crew of volunteers at four plant
 ings during the fall and winter. It's a great way to find out why volunteer
 s love our crew leaders!  Contact Andy at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or 503-2
 82-8846 x24 for more information.\n\nIf you live in the Brooklyn or Sellwoo
 d-Moreland neighborhoods\, you can order trees to plant on Nov. 21. Just cl
 ick on "Order Street & Yard Trees" to create your online account by Sept. 2
 1. You can order yard trees right away\, and you can order a tree for your 
 parking strip after the city completes the inspection and permitting requir
 ed for planting there. Questions? E-mail your neighborhood coordinator Seth
  (for Brooklyn) at BrooklynNeighborhoodTrees@gmail.com or Laurie (for Sellw
 ood-Moreland) at SellwoodMorelandTreePlanting@yahoo.com.
