 h Beaverton! We will be planting dozens of large (6-10' tall) trees at thei
 r new homes\, and your help is what makes this community planting possible!
 </span></p><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting
  crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guida
 nce\, as well as light breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate. We as
 k that all volunteers dress for the weather\, wear sturdy shoes/boots you d
 on't mind getting dirty\, and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>How do I regis
 ter? </b>Pre-Registration is now closed but planters are still needed\, jus
 t simply show up and sign-in when you arrive!</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We
  request that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 1
