 th waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> signed by th
 eir parent/guardian.</p><p><b>Private transportation</b>: You will travel f
 rom the meeting location to a few planting sites in the nearby neighborhood
  (up to several miles). <b>We recommend private transportation</b> (bike or
  vehicle)\, but there may be an option to carpool if others in your small p
 lanting crew are also comfortable with this. </p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Plea
 se check out our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" 
 target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u
 ></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  
 You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.or
 g" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org<
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213. We look forward to 
