DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer! \n\nPlease arrive by 
 8:45am and we'll provide coffee and doughnuts to get your started. We'll al
 so provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for 
 the weather and wearing sturdy shoes. \n\nWe encourage you to bring a blank
  white t-shirt to receive a freshly silk-screened\, one of a kind 2012 FoT 
 Neighborhood Tree Planting t-shirt. The neighborhood group will also provid
 e a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete. Live m
 usic by Ten Spiders will accompany lunch!\n\nWe look forward to seeing you 
 out there! For more info\, contact Jesse at 503 282-8846 x520 or jesseb@fri
 endsoftrees.org.
