DESCRIPTION:Join our popular group of key volunteers! Sign up for our free 
 training to learn how to lead volunteer planters at morning tree plantings.
  As a trained crew leader\, you'll guide a crew of volunteers at four plant
 ings during the fall and winter. It's a great way to make new friends and f
 ind out why volunteers love our crew leaders! Contact Andy at AndyM@Friends
 ofTrees.org or 503-282-8846 x24 for more information.\n\nIf you live in the
  Village at Fisher's Landing or Fisher's Creek neighborhood and would like 
 to order trees to plant on Nov. 7\, click on "Order Street & Yard Trees" an
 d create your online account by Sept. 7. Please contact Lisa at sctahiti@co
 mcast.net if you have questions.
