DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\
 nTo find your tree\, click on 'Order Trees' on our home page and click 'Let
 's Get Started.'  Be sure to start this process by 12/17/12.\n\nPlease arri
 ve by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting s
 tarts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to 
 do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighb
 orhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers afte
 r the planting is complete.\n\nRSVPs are not required. Please contact Andy 
 or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more informati
 on. We look forward to seeing you out there!
