DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer -- or click <a href= h
 ttps://friendsoftrees.org/plant-it-programs>HERE</a> to purchase a tree for
  your home.\n\nPlease arrive to the staging site by 8:45am to enjoy some ho
 t coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We 
 provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the
  weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also p
 rovide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete.\n
 \n<b>Looking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for gr
 oups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://www.friendsoftrees.org/vo
 lunteer/group-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for gr
 oups of 4 or less.\n\nRiding your bike? Join one of our Bike Planting Crews
  at this planting: <a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/how-can
 -you-help/plant-trees-by-bike">sign up here!</a>\n\nPlease contact Jenny & 
 Randi at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more information.
   We look forward to seeing you out there!
