DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer -- or click <b><a href
 ="https://friendsoftrees.org/get-a-tree/" target="_blank">HERE</a></b> to p
 urchase a tree for your household. Dozens of large (6-10â tall) trees wil
 l be ready for planting in their new homes across these neighborhoods\, <u>
 and your help is what makes this community planting possible!</u><i><br></i
 ><br>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and enjoy some breakfast snacks and
  coffee\, tea\, or hot chocolate. The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. W
 e provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, so all you need to do is show up 
 dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots â and be ready 
 to have fun!&nbsp\; Our neighborhood volunteers with also provide a potluck
  lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete.<br><b></b><br><b>
 How do I register? </b>Online registration closes the day before the event\
 , but there is still space available -- please simply show up at 8:45am.<br
 >&nbsp\;<br><b>Have a pickup truck? </b>We need your help getting these you
 ng trees to their planting sites a few blocks away from the central staging
  site. Please sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/truck" targ
 et="_blank">www.friendsoftrees.org/truck</a> if you're able to help us out 
 in this key role.&nbsp\;<br><br><b>This event will have a bike planting cre
 w!</b> Want to join the bike team? Sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsof
 trees.org/bike" target="_blank">www.friendsoftrees.org/bike</a>. Bikers wit
 h trailers and cargo bikes are awesome\, but anyone with a bike is welcome 
 to take part!&nbsp\;<br><br><b>Under age 18?</b> A signed <a href="http://f
 riendsoftrees.org/images/stories/pdf/Youth_Waiver_2015.pdf" target="_blank"
 >youth waiver</a> is required for you to volunteer. We kindly request youth
  15 years and younger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Je
 nny\, Pablo\, and Carey at 503-595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friend
 softrees.org" target="_blank">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org </a>if you have 
 questions or need any further information. We look forward to seeing you ou
 t there!<br><br>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsor\, <a href="https://do
 ssierhotel.com/" target="_blank">Dossier</a>!<br>===&nbsp\;&nbsp\;
