DESCRIPTION:===================<br><br>We're grateful for the popular inter
 est in this event\, which is now <u><b>FULL and CLOSED</b></u> to further v
 olunteers.&nbsp\; Thank you for your interest\, and please consider support
 ing any of our open events this same day\, or in March!<br><br><br>========
 ===========<br>Join us in planting trees or click <b><a href="https://frien
 dsoftrees.org/get-a-tree/" target="_blank">HERE</a></b> to purchase a tree 
 for your household. Dozens of large (6-10â tall) trees will be ready for 
 planting in their new homes across these neighborhoods\, and <u>your help i
 s what makes this community planting possible!</u><br><br>Please arrive by 
 8:45am to sign-in and enjoy some breakfast snacks and coffee\, tea\, or hot
  chocolate. The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, too
 ls\, and guidance\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weathe
 r and wearing sturdy shoes or boots â and be ready to have fun!&nbsp\; Ou
 r neighborhood volunteers with also provide a potluck lunch for all volunte
 ers after the planting is complete.<br>&nbsp\;<br><b>Have a pickup truck?</
 b> We need your help getting these young trees to their planting sites a fe
 w blocks away from the central staging site. Please sign up at <a href="htt
 p://www.friendsoftrees.org/truck" target="_blank">www.friendsoftrees.org/tr
 uck</a> if you're able to help us out in this key role.<br><br><b>Under age
  18? </b>A signed <a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/images/stories/pdf/You
 th_Waiver_2015.pdf" target="_blank">youth waiver </a>is required for you to
  volunteer. We kindly request youth 15 years and younger are accompanied by
  an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at 503-595-0213 
 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank">volunteer@
 friendsoftrees.org</a> if you have questions or need any further informatio
 n. We look forward to seeing you out there!<br><br>===<br>Thank you to our 
 event sponsors\, <a href="https://www.portofportland.com/" target="_blank">
 Port of Portland</a>&nbsp\;and <a href="https://www.jfschmidt.com/" id="ow1
 295" __is_owner="true">J Frank Schmidt &amp\; Son Co.</a>&nbsp\;<br>===&nbs
