UID:bu6i73lit0c6rrfour7e6ik0g0@google.com
CREATED:20190808T153327Z
DESCRIPTION:Tree expert\, Jim Gersbach\, will talk about trees appropriate 
 for planting strips in PDX/Vancouver.  Come learn about all the trees\, and
  if you're a FOT customer\, bring the approved list for your planting strip
  to help choose your perfect tree.\n\nThis presentation is FREE and light r
 efreshments will be provided. \n\nOur presenter\, Jim Gersbach\, has volunt
 eered in many\, many capacities with Friends of Trees for almost two decade
 s now. Jim has an incredible range of knowledge about Portland's urban fore
 st--from how different species tolerate our specific urban climate to what 
 trees grow where across the city. Further\, he has been inspired to travel 
 far and wide to visit noteworthy trees across the country and beyond. He is
  also the visionary behind the Ainsworth Linear Arboretum that runs for nea
 rly 2 miles along NE Ainsworth St. from MLK Blvd. to Fernhill Park. As a la
 bor of love\, Jim has not only planted dozens of rare and unusual trees her
 e\, but he has hand watered them through many a hot summer. \n\nSo\, come l
 earn from an expert and choose your perfect tree.\n\nAlready found your per
 fect tree?  Order your tree now at friendsoftrees.org\, give us a call at 5
 03-595-0212 to place your order over the phone.\n
