DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer -- or click <a href= h
 ttps://friendsoftrees.org/plant-it-programs>HERE</a> to purchase a tree for
  your home.\n\nPlease arrive to the staging site by 8:45am to enjoy some ho
 t coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We 
 provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the
  weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also p
 rovide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete. \
 n\n<b>Looking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for g
 roups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volun
 teering/group-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for in
 dividuals or groups of 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\n<b>This eve
 nt will have people planting trees by bike! Want to join the bike team?</b>
  Sign up <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/how-can-you-help/pl
 ant-trees-by-bike>HERE.</a> Bikers with trailers and cargo bikes are awesom
 e and everyone with a bike is welcome to take part of our bike planting eff
 orts.\n\nPlease contact our Volunteer & Outreach Team at (503) 595-0213 if 
 you have any questions or need more information. We look forward to seeing 
 you out there!\n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!\n\n<b>Thank you 
 to Dragonfly Coffee House for generously sponsoring this event!<b>\n\n
