DESCRIPTION:<p><b>===============</b></p><p>Due to the current snowy/icy co
 nditions\, our tree nursery deliveries have been postponed due to potential
 ly hazardous roads. Unfortunately\, this means the <b><u>Cedar Mill / Cedar
  Hills planting is canceled</u></b>.  If you are receiving trees or otherwi
 se involved in this event please look for communications from our staff.  T
 hank you for your patience and understanding with this change of plans!</p>
 <p><b>===============</b></p><p>Let's plant trees together in the Cedar Mil
 l and Cedar Hills neighborhoods! Click <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftree
 s.org/get-a-tree/" target="_blank"><u><u><u>HERE</u></u></u></a></u></b> to
  purchase a tree for your household. Dozens of large (6-10' tall) trees wil
 l be ready for planting in their new homes\, and your help is what makes th
 is community planting possible!</p><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in an
 d be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gl
 oves\, tools\, and guidance\, as well as light breakfast snacks and coffee/
 tea/hot chocolate. We ask that all volunteers dress for the weather\, wear 
 sturdy shoes/boots you don't mind getting dirty\, and be ready to have fun!
 </p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request that youth 15 and under volunteer wi
 th a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their own and wi
 ll need to hand us a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver" 
 target="_blank"><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></a></u></b> signed by their
  parent/guardian.</p><p><b>Private transportation</b>: You will travel from
  the meeting location to a few planting sites in the nearby neighborhood (u
 p to several miles). <b>We recommend private transportation</b> (bike or ve
 hicle)\, but there may be an option to carpool if others in your small plan
 ting crew are also comfortable with this.</p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please c
 heck out our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" targ
 et="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u></u></u>
 </a></u></b>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Je
 nny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><b>
 <u><u><u><u><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></u></u></u></u></b></u></a>
 \, 503-595-0213. We look forward to planting together soon!</p><p>===<br>Th
 ank you to our event sponsors <a href="https://portlandgeneral.com/" target
 ="_blank"><u><u>Portland General Electric</u></u></a> &amp\; <a href="https
 ://www.hamptonlumber.com/">Hampton Lumber</a>.</p><p>===</p><p><br></p><b><
 hr /></b><p></p><p>This event is in partnership with Clean Water Services.<
 /p>
