DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer -- or click <a href= h
 ttps://friendsoftrees.org/plant-it-programs>HERE</a> to purchase a tree for
  your home. We are still confirming the staging site for this planting so s
 tay tuned!\n\nPlease arrive to the staging site by 8:45am to enjoy some hot
  coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We p
 rovide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the 
 weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also pr
 ovide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete!\n\
 n<b>Looking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for gro
 ups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunte
 ering/group-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for indi
 viduals or groups of 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nPlease contac
 t Jenny & Randi at (503) 595-0213 if you have questions or need any further
  information.\n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!
