DESCRIPTION:Volunteer to join a small work party planting 5-10 trees (6-10f
 t tall) throughout Westside Vancouver neighborhoods. FOT staff and voluntee
 rs will meet on Thursday morning at Esther Short Park at 9:45am. We'll brea
 k into a few teams\, head out at 10am to plant some trees\, and return to t
 he park at 12:30pm.<br><br><b>How do I register?</b> Online registration ha
 s closed\, but there is still room at this event.  Please simply show up an
 d sign-in when you arrive!<br><u></u><br><u></u><b>Under age 18?</b> We req
 uest that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 an
 d older can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us a <b><u><a href
 ="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><
 u><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u
 ></u></u></u></a></u></b> signed by their parent/guardian.<p><b>What about 
 event safety?</b> We <u>require</u> that all people at our events cancel if
  you are feeling unwell or have been exposed to someone who tested positive
  for Covid-19 within 3 days of the event.  For our safety recommendations a
 nd more\, visit the <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq
 /"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer Frequently Asked 
 Questions webpage</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></
 u></a></u></b>.  </p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our <b><u><a hr
 ef="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><
 u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  Yo
 u can reach Gabriel and Jenny at <b><u><a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoft
 rees.org"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>volunteer@friendsoft
 rees.<wbr />org</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u>
 </a></u></b> We look forward to planting together soon!</p>
