 ">Woodhaven City Park</a> event in Sherwood! We hope that you can join us t
 here this Saturday at 8:45am!<br><br>======================================
 =================================<br><br>Join us in planting trees as a vol
 unteer -- or click <b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/get-a-tree/" targ
 et="_blank">HERE</a></b> to purchase a tree for your household. Dozens of l
 arge (6-10â tall) trees will be ready for planting in their new homes acr
 oss these neighborhoods\, <u>and your help is what makes this community pla
 nting possible!</u><br><u><br></u>Please arrive by 12:15pm to sign-in and e
 njoy a warm lunch before we get started planting. The planting starts promp
 tly at 12:30pm. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, so all you need 
 to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots 
 â and be ready to have fun!&nbsp\;<br>&nbsp\;<br><b>Have a pickup truck? 
 </b>We need your help getting these young trees to their planting sites a f
 ew blocks away from the central staging site. Please sign up at <a href="ht
 tp://www.friendsoftrees.org/truck" target="_blank">www.friendsoftrees.org/t
 ruck</a> if you're able to help us out in this key role.&nbsp\;<br><br><b>T
 his event will have a bike planting crew! </b>Want to join the bike team? S
 ign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/bike" target="_blank">www.
