DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! Nei
 ghborhoods being planting this day are:  Burton Ridge\, Ellsworth Springs\,
  Forest Ridge\, Marrion\, Meadow Homes\, Oakbrook\, Ogden\, Vancouver Heigh
 ts.\n\nTo find your tree\, click on 'Order Trees' on our home page and clic
 k 'Let's Get Started.'  Be sure to start this process by 12/10/12.\n\nPleas
 e arrive by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The plan
 ting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you ne
 ed to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our 
 neighborhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteer
 s after the planting is complete.\n\nRSVPs are not required. Please contact
  Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more inf
 ormation. We look forward to seeing you out there! \n\n
