DESCRIPTION:<br><b>**Tree caller night is CANCELLED\, see you next week!**<
 /b><br><br><br>Volunteer to help grow greener neighborhoods by joining a Fr
 iends of Trees staff member in calling our âtreecipientsâ to help them 
 pick out new trees for their homes and streets. Youâll learn about the di
 fferent types of trees available through FOT planting programs\, and how to
  help neighbors navigate the FOT website and tree ordering process.<br>This
  role directly contributes to our ability to plant more trees in neighborho
 ods. A short training is required -- and youâll be asked to commit to at 
 least three Wednesday evenings at our office at 3117 NE MLK Blvd in NE Port
 land.<br><br>Email our Volunteer &amp\; Outreach team at <a href="mailto:vo
 lunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a
 > to join in!
