DESCRIPTION:<u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><p><b>===========</b></p><p><b>Due 
 to popular support\, this event is now <u>full and closed</u>.&nbsp\; </b>P
 lease consider any future open event - we hope to plant with you soon!</p><
 p><b>===========</b></p><p><b>Let's plant trees together in the South Beave
 rton neighborhood!</b><span>&nbsp\;Forty&nbsp\;large (6-10' tall) trees wil
 l be ready for planting in their new homes at this event\, and your help is
  what makes this community planting possible!</span></p><p>Please arrive by
  8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 
 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, as well as light breakfa
 st snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate. We ask that all volunteers dress fo
 r the weather\, wear sturdy shoes/boots you don't mind getting dirty\, and 
 be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b>&nbsp\;We request that yout
 h 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.&nbsp\; Youth 16 and older 
 can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us a&nbsp\;<b><u><a href="
 http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver"><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></a><
 /u></b>&nbsp\;signed by their parent/guardian.</p><p><b>What about Covid-19
 ?</b>&nbsp\;We&nbsp\;<u>require</u>&nbsp\;that people cancel their particip
 ation if you are feeling unwell or have been exposed to someone who tested 
 positive for Covid-19 within 3 days of the event.&nbsp\; We&nbsp\;<u>recomm
 end</u>&nbsp\;everyone is fully-vaccinated\, bring and wear a face mask whe
 n working in close quarters\, and respect 6’ of physical distance. Please s
 ee our&nbsp\;<b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u><
 u>Volunteer Frequently Asked Questions webpage</u></u></a></u></b>&nbsp\;fo
 r more details.&nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\;&nbsp\;<br></p><p><b>Question
 s?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please check out our&nbsp\;<b><u><a href="https://frien
 dsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></a></u></
 b>.&nbsp\; Our team is also happy to assist!&nbsp\; You can reach Gabriel a
 nd Jenny at&nbsp\;<b><u><a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><u><u
 >volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></u></a></u></b>&nbsp\;We look forward to 
 planting together soon!</p><b><hr></b><p>This event is in partnership with 
 the City of Beaverton.</p><p>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsor&nbsp\;<a
  href="https://dudek.com/"><u><u><u>Dudek</u></u></u></a>.<br>===<br></p><u
 ></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>
