  a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete.<br>&nbs
 p\;<br><b>Have a pickup truck? </b>We need your help getting these young tr
 ees to their planting sites a few blocks away from the central staging site
 . Please sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/truck" target="_
 blank">www.friendsoftrees.org/truck</a> if you're able to help us out in th
 is key role.&nbsp\;<br><br><b>This event will have a bike planting crew!</b
 > Want to join the bike team? Sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees
 .org/bike" target="_blank">www.friendsoftrees.org/bike</a>. Bikers with tra
 ilers and cargo bikes are awesome\, but anyone with a bike is welcome to ta
 ke part!&nbsp\;<br><br><b>Under age 18?</b> A signed <a href="http://friend
 softrees.org/images/stories/pdf/Youth_Waiver_2015.pdf" target="_blank">yout
 h waiver</a> is required for you to volunteer. We kindly request youth 15 y
 ears and younger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny\,
