DESCRIPTION:20 new trees will be planted on the grounds of Hoover Elementar
 y and the adjacent city park in celebration of arbor day!  \n\nPlease arriv
 e by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  We encourage vo
 lunteers of all ages to come help out. The planting starts promptly at 9:00
 am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed 
 for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes. This planting is partnership with
  the City of Salem and the Salem-Keizer School district.\n\nRSVPs are not r
 equired. Please contact Elizabeth at (503)467-2527 if you have any question
 s or need more information. We look forward to seeing you out there! 
