LOCATION:13200 NE LeRoy Haagen Memorial Drive\, Vancouver\, WA 98684\, USA
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:NE Vancouver neighborhood planting (Vancouver\, WA)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
