 required 3.5 hour training. Breakfast refreshments and a t-shirt will be pr
 ovided. <br><br>Any questions? Please don't hesitate to be in touch with Ca
 rey\, Pablo\, or Jenny in our Volunteer &amp\; Outreach Program: Volunteer@
