  hundreds of street and yard trees a new home.\n\nPlease arrive to the stag
 ing site by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The plan
 ting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and planting gu
 idance so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing
  sturdy shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lun
 ch for all volunteers after the planting is complete!\n\n<b>Looking to volu
 nteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for groups of more than 5 
 people - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/group-registr
 ation>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for individuals or groups o
 f 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nPlease contact Jenny & Randi at 
 (503) 595-0213 if you have questions or need any further information.\n\nWe
  look forward to seeing you out there!
