 ide Woods\, Fircrest\, First Place\, Hearthwood\, Image\, Kevanna Park\, La
 ndover-Sharmel\, North Hearthwood\, North Image\, Parkside\, and Parkway Ea
 st.\n\nPlease arrive to the staging site by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee
  and breakfast treats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide 
 gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather
  and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also provide a
  potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete. \n\n<b>Du
 e to popular community interest\, this event is now full and closed to unre
 gistered volunteer groups of 5 people or more. </b>  RSVPs are not required
  for individuals -- you may simply show up!\n\nPlease contact our Volunteer
  & Outreach Team at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more i
