DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees <b><a href="https://www.tfaforms.com/
 4694015?tfa_26=a0Tf4000003IH8d&tfa_28=Madison%20South/Rose%20City%20Park/Su
 mner/Woodland%20Park\,%20NE%20Portland&tfa_31=a0Vf40000045IZM&tfa_45=Tree%2
 0Planter\,%201/19/2019%208:45AM%20&tfa_47=2019-01-19&tfa_49=4&tfa_59=Standa
 rd%20FOT&tfa_51=offsite" target="_blank">as a volunteer</a></b> -- or click
  <b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/get-a-tree/" target="_blank">HERE</
 a></b> to purchase a tree for your household. Dozens of large (6-10â tall
 ) trees will be ready for planting in their new homes across these neighbor
 hoods\, <u>and your help is what makes this community planting possible!</u
 ><i><br></i><br>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and enjoy some breakfast
  snacks and coffee\, tea\, or hot chocolate. The planting starts promptly a
 t 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, so all you need to do 
 is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots â an
 d be ready to have fun!&nbsp\; Our neighborhood volunteers with also provid
 e a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete.<br><b>
 </b><br><b>How do I register?</b> All individuals and groups are kindly ask
 ed to RSVP to save your spot(s) by filling out our quick <a href="https://w
 ww.tfaforms.com/4694015?tfa_26=a0Tf4000003IH8d&tfa_28=Madison%20South/Rose%
 20City%20Park/Sumner/Woodland%20Park\,%20NE%20Portland&tfa_31=a0Vf40000045I
 ZM&tfa_45=Tree%20Planter\,%201/19/2019%208:45AM%20&tfa_47=2019-01-19&tfa_49
 =4&tfa_59=Standard%20FOT&tfa_51=offsite" target="_blank"><b>Registration Fo
 rm</b></a>. Registration is highly recommended but not required.<br>&nbsp\;
 <br><b>Have a pickup truck? </b>We need your help getting these young trees
  to their planting sites a few blocks away from the central staging site. P
 lease sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/truck" target="_bla
 nk">www.friendsoftrees.org/truck</a> if you're able to help us out in this 
 key role.&nbsp\;<br><br><b>This event will haveâ âaâ âbikeâ âpl
 anting crew!</b> Want to join the bike team? Sign up at <a href="http://www
 .friendsoftrees.org/bike">www.friendsoftrees.org/bike</a>. Bikers with trai
 lers and cargo bikes are awesome\,â âbutâ âanyoneâ âwith a bike
  is welcome to take part!&nbsp\;<br><br><b>Under age 18?</b> A signed <a hr
 ef="http://friendsoftrees.org/images/stories/pdf/Youth_Waiver_2015.pdf" tar
 get="_blank">youth waiver</a> is required for you to volunteer. We kindly r
 equest youth 15 years and younger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Pleas
 e contact Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at 503-595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volu
 nteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org </a>
 if you have questions or need any further information. We look forward to s
 eeing you out there!
