DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\
 nTo find your tree\, click on 'Order Street & Yard Trees' on our home page 
 and click 'Get Started.' Be sure you answer the questions at "get started" 
 by 2/6/2012. \n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am and we'll provide coffee and dough
 nuts to get your started. We'll also provide gloves and tools\, so all you 
 need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes. The
  neighborhood group will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers af
 ter the planting in complete. \n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there! 
  RSVPs are not required.  Please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees
 .org or (503) 595-0213 for more information.
