DESCRIPTION:<p>Let's plant trees together in Hillsboro! Interested in recei
 ving a tree? Click <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/get-a-tree/" t
 arget="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u>HERE</u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> t
 o purchase a tree for your household. Dozens of large (6-10' tall) trees wi
 ll be ready for planting in their new homes\, and your help is what makes t
 his community planting possible!</p><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in a
 nd be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide g
 loves\, tools\, and guidance\, as well as light breakfast snacks and coffee
 /tea/hot chocolate. We ask that all volunteers dress for the weather\, wear
  sturdy shoes/boots you don't mind getting dirty\, and be ready to have fun
 !</p><p><b>How do I register? </b>Online registration has closed at this ti
 me\, but there is still room at this event. Please simply show-up and sign 
 in at the welcome table!</p><p><b>Have a pickup truck?</b> We need your hel
 p getting these young trees to their planting sites a few blocks away from 
 the central staging site. <b><a href="https://www.tfaforms.com/4840511?tfa_
 26=a0TPa00000qajaQ&tfa_2189=Calle%20Diez%20and%20Downtown%20Hillsboro%20nei
 ghborhood%20planting\,%20Hillsboro&tfa_31=a0VPa000008zJZC&tfa_45=Truck%20Dr
 iver\,%20%20at%20December%206\,%202025%20at%208:30%20am&tfa_2190=2025-12-06
 &tfa_49=4.5&tfa_886=Standard%20FOT&tfa_51=offsite" target="_blank"><u><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u>Please sign up</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></
 b> if you're able to help in this key role. <br><br><b>Under age 18?</b> We
  request that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 1
 6 and older can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us a <b><u><a 
 href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u
 ><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> signed by their p
 arent/guardian.</p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our <b><u><a href
 ="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u
 ><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is
  also happy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Vol
 unteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u>volunteer@frie
 ndsoftrees.org</u></u></u></u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213. We look forward 
 to planting together soon!</p><p><b>What neighborhoods will the trees be pl
 anted in?</b> Calle Diez &amp\; Downtown Hillsboro</p><b><hr /></b><p></p><
 p>This event made possible through a grant from the Arbor Day Foundation.</
 p>
