DESCRIPTION:Morning Star Missionary Baptist Church\n\nJoin us in planting t
 rees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\nTo find your tree\, click on 'Or
 der Street & Yard Trees' on our home page and click 'Get Started.' Be sure 
 you answer the questions at "get started" by 2/27/2012. \n\nPlease arrive b
 y 8:45am and we'll provide coffee and doughnuts to get your started. We'll 
 also provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed fo
 r the weather and wearing sturdy shoes. The neighborhood group will also pr
 ovide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting in complete. Th
 is planting is generously sponsored by the Port of Portland.\n\nWe look for
 ward to seeing you out there!  RSVPs are not required.  Please contact Andy
  Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 for more information.
