DESCRIPTION:Neighbors will plant trees in their neighborhood. Click on "Ord
 er Street & Yard Trees" to set up an account to buy trees for your yard or 
 parking strip.\n\nOnce you set up an account\, Friends of Trees will arrang
 e for the city of Portland to inspect the planting site and issue a permit.
  For this planting\, you must create your account by Dec 15 and order your 
 trees by Jan 26.\n\nQuestions? Contact your Neighborhood Coordinator.\n\nBo
 ise: Andrew\, 503-679-9796 or boise_trees@yahoo.com.\n\nEliot: Clint\, 503-
 552-8678 or trees@eliotneighborhood.org.\n\nHumboldt: Breanne or Laura at h
 umboldtfot@gmail.com.\n\nKing: Irek\, 503-793-2114 or panirek@yahoo.com.\n\
 nPiedmont: Kathleen\, 503-285-0997 or rowlands-rugge@hotmail.com.\n\nSabin:
  Irek\, 503-793-2114 or panirek@yahoo.com.\n\nThis planting is sponsored by
  Con-way and the East Multnomah Soil & Water Conservation District.
