 ariety of native trees and shrubs\, and as usual\, we encourage volunteers 
 of all ages to come help out. The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We pr
 ovide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the w
 eather and wearing sturdy shoes. This planting is generously sponsored by K
 aiser Permanente.\n\nRSVPs are not required. Please contact Andy or Jenny a
 t (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more information. We loo
 k forward to seeing you out there! 
