DESCRIPTION:Crew Leaders are trained volunteers who are crucial to plant tr
 ees properly and lead groups of volunteers at more than 70 different planti
 ng events this planting season.  Friends of Trees is aiming to plant more t
 han 4\,500 street and yard trees in our award-winning Neighborhood Trees pr
 ogram.  Help us make those goals a reality and register to become a crew le
 ader with us!  Pre-registration for this training is required.  \n\nYou can
  sign-up <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/2012-08-29-17-
 44-58/nt-crew-leader-training">HERE.</a>\n\n
