DESCRIPTION:Please note: this planting is FULL and we're not accepting grou
 p registration.  Individual volunteers are still welcome\, though!\n\nJoin 
 us in planting trees at our April 21st Greenway planting in honor of Earth 
 Day!  We'll be planting on NE 37th and NE 38th between NE Hancock and NE Ho
 lman.  Please stay tuned for the exact meet-up location\, it has yet to be 
 determined.\n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am and we'll provide coffee and doughnu
 ts to get your started. We'll also provide gloves\, tools\, and tree planti
 ng guidance\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and 
 wearing sturdy shoes and we'll assign you to a planting team led by one of 
 our trained Crew Leaders. Help us green the Greenways! We look forward to s
 eeing you out there! RSVPs are not required. \n\nContact Andy Meeks at Andy
 M@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 for more information.
