 inated\, bring and wear a face mask when working in close quarters\, and re
 spect 6’ of physical distance. Please see our&nbsp\;<b><u><a href="https://
 friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u>Volunteer Frequently Asked Questions 
 webpage</u></a></u></b>&nbsp\;for more details.&nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbs
 p\;&nbsp\;<br></p><p><b>Questions?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please check out our&nb
 sp\;<b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u>Volunteer 
 FAQ webpage</u></a></u></b>.&nbsp\; Our team is also happy to assist!&nbsp\
 ; You can reach Gabriel and Jenny at&nbsp\;<b><u><a href="mailto:Volunteer@
 friendsoftrees.org"><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></a></u></b>&nbsp\;W
 e look forward to planting together soon!</p><b><hr></b><p>This event is in
  partnership with the City of Beaverton.<br></p><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u
