DESCRIPTION:Join us the day "The Lorax" movie is released to plant real tre
 es in Portland! Tickets to the movie provided by Whole Foods Market will be
  handed out to volunteers who answer Treevia questions about Dr. Seuss' boo
 k\, "The Lorax."\n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am\, and we'll provide coffee and 
 doughnuts to get your started. We'll also provide gloves and tools\, so all
  you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes
 . The neighborhood group will also provide a potluck lunch for all voluntee
 rs after the planting in complete. This planting is generously sponsored by
  Portland General Electric and Whole Foods Market.\n\nWe look forward to se
 eing you out there!  RSVPs are not required.  Please contact Andy Meeks at 
 AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 for more information.
