 l host at least 4 major plantings in neighborhoods and natural areas and we
  need help to lead those volunteers!  Make a difference greening the Salem 
 community\, learn more about trees\, and meet some fun people while you're 
 at it as a Salem Crew Leader!\n\n<b>Due to high demand\, this training is n
 ow FULL</b> Thank you for your support!  Please consider joining us instead
  at the first Salem tree planting of the season on Sat\, Nov 7th!\n\nContac
 t Jenny & Randi with any questions or for further information at Volunteer@
