CREATED:20190808T153327Z
DESCRIPTION:Friends of Trees returns to Oregon City to plant trees in the M
 cLoughlin\, Barclay Hills\, and Rivercrest Neighborhoods!\n\nJoin us in pla
 nting trees as a volunteer -- or click <a href= https://friendsoftrees.org/
 plant-it-programs>HERE</a> to purchase a tree for your home.\n\nPlease arri
 ve to the staging site by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast tre
 ats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\,
  so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturd
 y shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for
  all volunteers after the planting is complete.\n\n<b>Looking to volunteer 
 as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for groups of more than 5 people
  - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/group-registration>
 HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for individuals or groups of 4 or
  fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nPlease contact Jenny & Randi at (503) 
 595-0213 if you have questions or need any further information.\n\nWe look 
 forward to seeing you out there!\n\n<b>Thank you to J Frank Schmidt & Son C
 o for sponsoring this event!<b>\n\n
