DESCRIPTION:Overwhelmed by the choices? Let our Tree Matching Expert\, Jim 
 Gersbach help you find your "soil"mate. The right tree is out there\, let u
 s help you find it.\n\nJim will be helping SE Portland neighbors find their
  perfect tree. The presentation is free\, and light refreshments will be pr
 ovided. \n\nBar Carlo will also be open to provide additional beverage need
 s.\n\nJim is a long-time Friends of Trees volunteer and will share informat
 ion\, photos and fun facts about the trees FOT is offering this year. Jim h
 as an incredible range of knowledge about Portland's urban forest--from how
  different species tolerate our specific urban climate to what trees grow w
 here across the city. \n\nFurther\, he has been inspired to travel far and 
 wide to visit noteworthy trees across the country and beyond.\n\nHe is also
  the visionary behind the Ainsworth Linear Arboretum that runs for nearly 2
  miles along NE Ainsworth St. from MLK Blvd. to Fernhill Park. As a labor o
 f love\, Jim has not only planted dozens of rare and unusual trees here\, b
 ut he has hand watered them through many a hot summers. \n\nThere is no tim
 e like the present to order trees for the upcoming Friends of Trees Plantin
 g Day in YOUR neighborhood! \n\nEvery year we sell out of a number of tree 
 species\, so log-in at FriendsOfTrees.org to select and order your top pick
 s as soon as possible! \n\nIf you need assistance in making a selection\, b
 ut cannot make this presentation\, give us a call at 503-595-0212.
LAST-MODIFIED:20190808T155127Z
LOCATION:Bar Carlo (6433 SE Foster Rd)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Speed (Tree) Dating â Find your perfect tree match!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
