DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\
 nTo find your tree\, click on 'Order Street & Yard Trees' on our home page 
 and click 'Get Started.' Be sure you answer the questions at "get started" 
 by 1/16/2012. \n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am and we'll provide coffee and doug
 hnuts to get your started. We'll also provide gloves and tools\, so all you
  need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes. Th
 e neighborhood group will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers a
 fter the planting in complete. This planting is generously sponsored by Rec
 ology.\n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!  RSVPs are not required.
   Please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 f
 or more information.
