DESCRIPTION:LOCATION:  Kaiser Permanente Town Hall\n\nOur Crew Leaders are 
 essential to the success of our programs and must be able to help us plant 
 trees at least 3 times during our planting season.\n\nThe training will con
 sist of two sessions: a classroom-style session from 6:30 - 9:00pm on Thurs
 day\, January 28th and participation in a regular Friends of Trees planting
  on Saturday\, January 30th (8:15am - 1:00pm). \n\nYou need to be able to a
 ttend both sessions in order to become an Assistant Crew Leader.\n\nSpace i
 s limited - please follow this link to register in advance:  https://spread
 sheets.google.com/viewform?formkey=dG5BWEdCR19nS0RRWDYtUVhWeFlIUHc6MA
