DESCRIPTION:Please meet at the Kaiser Permanente Town Hall by 8:45am to vol
 unteer for this planting. If you have any questions\, please contact Andy M
 eeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or 503-282-8846 x24.\n\nThis planting will
  also include a training for new crew leaders. For information about how to
  register for the training\, contact Greg at gregt@friendsoftrees.org.\n\nT
 o order trees for your yard or parking strip\, click on "Order Street & Yar
 d Trees" to create your online account by Nov. 30. You can order yard trees
  right away\, and you can order trees for your parking strip after the city
  completes the inspection and permitting required for planting trees there.
  Questions? E-mail your neighborhood coordinator Kria (for Arbor Lodge) at 
 kria.lacher@gmail.com\, or Cynthia (for Overlook) at csulaski@comcast.net.\
 n\nThis planting is sponsored by Adidas.
