DESCRIPTION:Anyone who hasn't organized a neighborhood tree planting with F
 riends of Trees but wants to plan one for the fall or winter should attend 
 this free training. You'll learn how to use Friends of Trees' web-based ord
 ering and tracking system\, and you'll learn ways to inspire and assist you
 r neighbors as they order trees for their yards and parking strips. All who
  attend this training should plan to attend the follow-up training on Thurs
 day\, July 23rd\, from 6 to 8 p.m.\, to network with people who have coordi
 nated plantings in the past and to learn new organizing tools. Pre-registra
 tion is required. Contact Greg Tudor at gregt@friendsoftrees.org or 503-282
 -8846 ext. 12. 
