DESCRIPTION:Please join us in planting trees at our April 7th Greenway Plan
 ting! We'll be planting trees along the bike boulevard running from NE Hass
 alo to SE Bush via 86th and 87th Avenues. Please arrive by 8:45am and we'll
  provide coffee and doughnuts to get your started. We'll also provide glove
 s\, tools\, and tree planting guidance\, so all you need to do is show up d
 ressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and we'll assign you to a p
 lanting team led by one of our trained Crew Leaders. Help us green the Gree
 nways!\n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!  RSVPs are not required.
   Please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 f
 or more information.
