 ees properly and lead groups of volunteers at more than 80 different planti
 ng events this planting season.  In the Salem community we'll host at least
  4 major plantings in neighborhoods and natural areas and we need help to l
 ead those volunteers!  Make a difference greening the Salem community\, lea
 rn more about trees\, and meet some fun people while you're at it as a Sale
 m Crew Leader!\n\nRegistration is now full for this event.  Thank you for y
 our interest!  Please consider joining instead at our first Salem planting 
 of the season on Saturday\, Nov. 15th! \n\nEmail Jenny & Ian with any quest
 ions or for further information at Volunteer@FriendsofTrees.org.\n\n
