  click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/group-registration>HE
 RE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for individuals or groups of 4 or f
 ewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nAre you under age 18 and planting withou
 t your parent/guardian?  A signed <a href=http://www.friendsoftrees.org/ima
 ges/stories/pdf/Youth_Waiver_2015.pdf>youth waiver</a> is required for you 
 to volunteer. We kindly request youth 15 years and younger are accompanied 
 by an adult.\n\nPlease contact Jenny & Pablo at (503) 595-0213 if you have 
 questions or need any further information.  We look forward to seeing you o
 ut there!\n\n<i>Accessible on Bus Line 33.  For more directions\, visit <a 
 href=https://trimet.org/>https://trimet.org/</a>.</i>
