 d issue a permit. For this planting\, you must create your account by Dec 1
  and order your trees by Jan 12.\n\nQuestions? Contact your Neighborhood Co
 ordinator:\nArbor Lodge: Kria\, 503-548-4495 or kriagreenrealtor@gmail.com.
