 w.friendsoftrees.org/truck</a></b> if you're able to help us out in this ke
 y role.&nbsp\;<br><br><b><u>This event will have a bike crew!</u> </b>Want 
 to join the team planting trees by bike? Sign up at <b><a href="http://www.
 friendsoftrees.org/bike">www.friendsoftrees.org/bike</a></b>. Bikers with t
 railers and cargo bikes are awesome but anyone with a bike is welcome to ta
 ke part!&nbsp\;<br><br><b><u>Under age 18?</u></b> A signed youth waiver is
  required for you to volunteer: <b><a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/y
 outhwaiver">www.friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver</a></b> We kindly request yo
 uth 15 years and younger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact
  Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at 503-595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@fri
 endsoftrees.org">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a> if you have questions or 
 need any further information. We look forward to seeing you out there!
