DESCRIPTION:Dozens of large (6-10â tall) trees will be ready for planting
  in their new homes across these neighborhoods\, <u>and your help is what m
 akes this community planting possible!</u>&nbsp\; This event was profiled o
 n Oregon Field Guide\, <a href="https://www.opb.org/television/programs/ofg
 /segment/oregon-friends-trees-cooperative-planting/" target="_blank">check 
 out the article and video</a> to see what this event is *really* like!<br><
 br>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and enjoy some breakfast snacks and c
 offee\, tea\, or hot chocolate. The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We 
 provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, so all you need to do is show up dr
 essed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots â and be ready to
  have fun!&nbsp\; Our neighborhood volunteers with also provide a potluck l
 unch for all volunteers after the planting is complete.<br><b></b><br><b>Ho
 w do I register?</b>&nbsp\;Online registration closes 24 hours in advance o
 f our events\, but this planting is still open to volunteers!&nbsp\; Please
  simply show up at 8:45am\, see you soon!<br>&nbsp\;<br><b>Have a pickup tr
 uck? </b>We need your help getting these young trees to their planting site
 s a few blocks away from the central staging site. Please sign up at <a hre
 f="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/truck" target="_blank">www.friendsoftrees.
 org/truck</a> if you're able to help us out in this key role.&nbsp\;<br><br
 ><b>This event will have a bike planting crew!</b> Want to join the bike te
 am? Sign up at <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/bike" target="_blank"
 >www.friendsoftrees.org/bike</a>. Bikers with trailers and cargo bikes are 
 awesome\, but anyone with a bike is welcome to take part!&nbsp\;<br><br><b>
 Under age 18?</b> A signed <a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/images/storie
 s/pdf/Youth_Waiver_2015.pdf" target="_blank">youth waiver</a> is required f
 or you to volunteer. We kindly request youth 15 years and younger are accom
 panied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at 503-
 595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank">v
 olunteer@friendsoftrees.org </a>if you have questions or need any further i
 nformation. We look forward to seeing you out there!<br><br>===<br>Thank yo
 u to our event sponsors\, <a href="https://www.jfschmidt.com/" target="_bla
 nk">J Frank Schmidt &amp\; Son Co.</a> &amp\; <a href="https://www.maletis.
 com/" target="_blank">Maletis Beverage</a>.<br>===&nbsp\; &nbsp\;&nbsp\;
