DESCRIPTION:Please meet at the staging site by 9am to volunteer for this pl
 anting. If you have any questions\, please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@Frie
 ndsofTrees.org or 503-282-8846 x24.\n\nTo order trees for your yard or park
 ing strip\, click on "Order Street & Yard Trees" to create your online acco
 unt by Nov. 30. You can order yard trees right away\, and you can order tre
 es for your parking strip after the city completes the inspection and permi
 tting required for planting trees there. Questions? E-mail your neighborhoo
 d coordinator Vinette (for Hazelwood) at vkscott@gmail.com.
