DESCRIPTION:<p><b>`````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
 </b></p><p><b>Due to popular interest\, this event is <u>full and closed. <
 /u></b></p><p><b><u>```````````````````````````````````````````````````````
 ```</u></b></p><p>Let's plant trees together in SE Vancouver! Interested in
  receiving a tree? Click <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/get-a-tr
 ee/" target="_blank"><u><u><u>HERE</u></u></u></a></u></b> to purchase a tr
 ee for your household. Dozens of large (6-10' tall) trees will be ready for
  planting in their new homes\, and your help is what makes this community p
 lanting possible!</p><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned 
 a planting crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\,
  and guidance\, as well as light breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocol
 ate. We ask that all volunteers dress for the weather\, wear sturdy shoes/b
 oots you don't mind getting dirty\, and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Unde
 r age 18?</b> We request that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/gu
 ardian.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their own and will need to han
 d us a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank
 "><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></a></u></b> signed by their parent
 /guardian.</p><p><b>Private transportation</b>: You will travel from the me
 eting location to a few planting sites in the nearby neighborhood (up to se
 veral miles). <b>We recommend private transportation</b> (bike or vehicle)\
 , but there may be an option to carpool if others in your small planting cr
 ew are also comfortable with this.</p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check ou
 t our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_bl
 ank"><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our te
 am is also happy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailt
 o:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><b><u><u><u><u>volunteer@fr
 iendsoftrees.org</u></u></u></u></b></a>\, 503-595-0213. We look forward to
  planting together soon!</p><b><hr /></b><p>This event is in partnership wi
 th the City of Vancouver.</p>
