 d issue a permit. For this planting\, you must create your account by Oct 1
 3 and order your trees by Nov 24.\n\nQuestions? Contact your Neighborhood C
 oordinator. \n\nBrentwood Darlington: Paul\, 503-775-9127 or p-rinehart@msn
 .com.\n\nFoster-Powell: Janelle\, 503-819-9322 or janellegeddes@gmail.com.\
