DESCRIPTION:We'll be planting 36 western red cedars on the campus of La Sal
 le Catholic College Prep High School and would love your help!\n\nPlease ar
 rive by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting
  starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you need t
 o do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes.\n\n**This
  planting has closed to additional group sign-ups.  Please consider joining
  us in Tualatin (easy access off I-5 and I-205) instead.**\n\nPlease contac
 t Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more in
 formation. \n\n<i>This planting is generously sponsored by Collier Arbor Ca
 re/Bartlett Tree Care.</i>\n\n
