DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer -- or click <a href="h
 ttps://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Ffriendsoftrees.org%2Fplant-it-pro
 grams&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1514326619383000&amp\;usg=AFQjCNHsee4rl6tx2yE8YsT-
 LfxhFMgFLA" target="_blank">HERE</a> to purchase a tree for your home.<br><
 br>Please arrive Lents Gilbert Church by 8:45am to enjoy some breakfast tre
 ats and hot coffee or chocolate. The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We
  provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for th
 e weather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots. Our neighborhood volunteers wi
 ll also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is co
 mplete.   <br><br><b>Looking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly 
 requested for groups of more than 5 people - click <a href="https://www.goo
 gle.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Ffriendsoftrees.org%2Fvolunteering%2Fgroup-regist
 ration&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1514326619383000&amp\;usg=AFQjCNEjZHJVpQjBJKA92_o
 RvWf1jdB0lg" target="_blank">HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for 
 individuals or groups of 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!<br><br>Are y
 ou under age 18 and planting without your parent/guardian?  A signed <a hre
 f="https://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.friendsoftrees.org%2Fimage
 s%2Fstories%2Fpdf%2FYouth_Waiver_2015.pdf&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=15143266193830
 00&amp\;usg=AFQjCNGTDZxc2lDZJRaTXxbLiWRbyoanTQ" target="_blank">youth waive
 r</a> is required for you to volunteer. We kindly request youth 15 years an
 d younger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny &amp\; P
 ablo at (503) 595-0213 if you have questions or need any further informatio
 n.<br><br>We look forward to seeing you out there!<br><br>===<br>Thank you 
 to our event sponsor\, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2F
 www.portlandgeneral.com%2F&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1514326619383000&amp\;usg=AFQ
