 is Neighborhood Greenway Planting! \n\nPlease arrive at 8:45am for registra
 tion\, coffee\, and breakfast pastries. Enter from N Vancouver between scho
 ol and gym\, or from N Williams behind the church. Meet in Cantwell Hall (i
 n the basement\, at NE corner of school).\n\nWe'll also provide gloves\, to
 ols\, and tree planting guidance\, so all you need to do is show up dressed
  for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and we'll assign you to a plantin
 g team led by one of our trained Crew Leaders. RSVPs are not required. \n\n
 Please contact Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 for more information. We loo
 k forward to seeing you out there! 
