DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees at our April 14th Greenway planting! 
  We'll be planting on Ankeny Street and Salmon Street from SE 16th through 
 SE 41st (picture a continuous square).  \n\nUnfortunately\, this planting i
 s full and we cannot accept new groups to this event.  Families and individ
 uals\, however\, are still encouraged to attend!\n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am
  and we'll provide coffee and doughnuts to get your started. We'll also pro
 vide gloves\, tools\, and tree planting guidance\, so all you need to do is
  show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and we'll assign 
