DESCRIPTION:Help us find forever homes for trees that didn’t get planted th
 is season! We’re offering our locally sourced\, high-quality shade trees at
  a discounted wholesale price. Lists of trees are not available prior to th
 e sale. First come\, first served.\n\nPlease note:\n\n- No planting assista
 nce or delivery is available.\n- Parking is limited to loading only - pleas
 e park on the street.\n- Trees must be picked up within a week\, or they wi
 ll be forfeited.\n\nDon’t miss this chance to bring home a beautiful tree a
 t a great price!
