DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer or tree purchaser! \n\
 nTo find your tree\, click on 'Order Trees' on our home page and click 'Let
 's Get Started.'  Be sure to start this process by 2/18/13.\n\nPlease arriv
 e by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting st
 arts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to d
 o is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighbo
 rhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after
  the planting is complete. This planting is generously sponsored by NW Natu
 ral.\n\nRSVPs are not required. Please contact Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0
 213 if you have any questions or need more information. We look forward to 
 seeing you out there!
