DESCRIPTION:Join the Summer Inspector Tree Team!\n\nSummer Inspectors learn
  how to properly assess the health of newly-planted street and yard trees. 
  The total time commitment is about 12 hours over four months\, including t
 his required 3.5 hour training.  Breakfast refreshments and a t-shirt will 
 be provided.  Please pre-register for this event by signing up <a href=http
 s://docs.google.com/a/friendsoftrees.org/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdfqTZqakwKKboiJg
 9NTSXPBhNgTqrq6JvqSLIAV03dbrpXkg/viewform>HERE</a>. \n\nAny questions?  Ple
 ase don't hesitate to be in touch with Jenny or Pablo in our Volunteer & Ou
 treach Program: Volunteer@FriendsofTrees.org // 503-595-0213.  We hope to w
 ork with you soon!\n
