DESCRIPTION:<b>Due to popular interest\, this event is now full and closed 
 for groups.</b> Please consider any of our future plantings that remain ope
 n.  RSVPs are not required for individuals or groups of 4 or fewer -- you c
 an simply show up!\n\nPlease arrive to the staging site by 8:45am to enjoy 
