CREATED:20250820T221300Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Let's plant trees together in Portland on the inner eastside
 !  Of special note: this event is held out of our office! Dozens of large (
 6-10' tall) trees will be ready for planting in their new homes\, and your 
 help is what makes this community planting possible!</p><p>Please arrive by
  8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 
 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, as well as light breakfa
 st snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate. We ask that all volunteers dress fo
 r the weather\, wear sturdy shoes/boots you don't mind getting dirty\, and 
 be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request that youth 15 a
 nd under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can voluntee
 r on their own and will need to hand us a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftr
 ees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u
 ></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> signed by their parent/guardian.</p><p><b
 >Private transportation</b>: You will travel from the meeting location to a
  few planting sites in the nearby neighborhood (up to several miles). <b>We
  recommend private transportation</b> (bike or vehicle)\, but there may be 
 an option to carpool if others in your small planting crew are also comfort
 able with this. </p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our <b><u><a hre
 f="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><
 u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team i
 s also happy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Vo
 lunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u>volunteer@fri
 endsoftrees.org</u></u></u></u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213. We look forward
  to planting together soon!</p><p><b>What neighborhoods will the trees be p
 lanted in?</b> Boise-Eliot\, Buckman\, Humboldt\, Kerns\, King\, and Lloyd 
 District.</p><p>===</p><p>Thank you to our event sponsor\, <a href="https:/
 /www.honltreecare.com/" target="_blank"><u><u><u>Honl Tree Care</u></u></u>
 </a>.</p><p>===</p><b><hr /></b><p></p><br><p>This event is in partnership 
 with Portland Urban Forestry.</p>
