  your home.\n\nPlease arrive to the staging site\, the Morningstar Missiona
 ry Baptist Church at 4927 NE 55th Ave\, by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee 
 and breakfast treats.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide g
 loves and tools\, so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather 
 and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also provide a 
 potluck lunch for all volunteers after the planting is complete. \n\n<b>Loo
 king to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for groups of 
 more than 5 people - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/g
 roup-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for individuals
  or groups of 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nPlease contact our V
 olunteer & Outreach Team at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or nee
 d more information. We look forward to seeing you out there!\n\nWe look for
 ward to seeing you out there!\n\n<b>Thank you to Whole Foods for generously
  sponsoring this planting event!<b>\n\n
