DESCRIPTION:For Volunteers: The church is between SE 38th and 39th on SE Br
 ooklyn. Meet on the 38th Ave. side. Register and get refreshments in the ch
 urch basement.\nTo order trees for your yard or parking strip\, click on "O
 rder Street & Yard Trees" and create your online account by Oct. 5. You can
  order yard trees right away\, and you can order trees for your parking str
 ip after the city completes the inspection and permitting required for plan
 ting the trees. Questions? E-mail your neighborhood coordinators Sara and C
 hris (Buckman) at saralouisebutcher@hotmail.com\, Jack (Hosford-Abernethy) 
 at jacklindas@att.net\, or Debbie (Richmond) at ddstoller@yahoo.com.
