 eam is also happy to assist! <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" 
 target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@fr<u></u>i
 endsoftrees.or<u></u>g</u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u><
 /a> / 503-595-0213 We look forward to working together soon!<br></p><p>===<
 /p><p>Thank you to our event sponsor <a href="https://supertrees.com/" targ
 et="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u>SuperTrees</u></u></u></u></u></a>.</p><p>===</p
 ><p><br></p><b><hr /></b><p></p><p>This event in partnership with City of O
