 es will arrange for the city of Portland to inspect the planting site and i
 ssue a permit. For this planting\, you must create your account by Dec 15 a
 nd order your trees by Feb 2.\n\nQuestions? Contact your Neighborhood Coord
 inator:\nAlameda: Reed\, clanhall@yahoo.com.\nGrant Park: Lynn\, lynnraube@
 integra.net.\nIrvington: Neil\, 503-288-3627 or galleoninc@aol.com.\nSulliv
 an's Gulch: Dana\, 503-751-0399 or dcrane@lclark.edu.\n\nThis planting is p
 roudly sponsored by NW Natural.
