DESCRIPTION:===============<u></u><u></u><u></u>======<br><br><b>Due to the
  large nature of this event\, and recommendations from our local health off
 icials to avoid spreading the Coronavirus\, <u>this event is now cancelled<
 /u>.</b>&nbsp\; If you were to receive a tree at this event please check yo
 ur email for more information from us.&nbsp\; We apologize for this inconve
 nience and ask for your understanding as we try to do what's best for our c
 ommunity's health!<br><br>========<u></u><u></u><u></u>=============&nbsp\;
 &nbsp\;<br><br>Please contact Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at 503-595-0213 // 
 <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org<
 /a> if you have questions or need any further information.&nbsp\;<br><br>==
 =&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<br>Thank you to our event sponsor&nbsp\;<a href="https://ww
 w.jfschmidt.com/">J Frank Schmidt &amp\; Son Co.</a>!&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<
 br>===&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;
