DESCRIPTION:Join us in planting trees as a volunteer -- or click <a href= h
 ttps://friendsoftrees.org/plant-it-programs>HERE</a> to purchase a tree for
  your home.  We are planting in all West Vancouver Neighborhoods\, includin
 g: Arnada\, Carter Park\, Edgewood Park\, Fourth Plain Village\, Fruit Vall
 ey\, Hough\, Lincoln\, Northwest\, Rose Village\, Shumway. \n\nPlease arriv
 e to the staging site by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast trea
 ts.  The planting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, 
 so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy
  shoes.  Our neighborhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for 
 all volunteers after the planting is complete!\n\n<b>Looking to volunteer a
 s a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for groups of more than 5 people 
 - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/group-registration>H
 ERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for individuals or groups of 4 or 
 fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nPlease contact Jenny & Randi at (503) 5
 95-0213 if you have questions or need any further information.\n\nWe look f
 orward to seeing you out there!
