 answer the questions at "get started" by 10/17/2011. \n\nWe'll provide glov
 es and tools and all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and 
 wearing sturdy shoes! For more info or if you have questions please contact
  Jesse at 503 282-8846 x20 or jesseb@friendsoftrees.org
