DESCRIPTION:Our Crew Leaders are essential to the success of our programs a
 nd must be able to help us plant trees at least 3 times during our planting
  season.\n\nThe training will consist of two sessions: a classroom-style se
 ssion from 6:30 - 8:30pm on Thursday\, January 27th and participation in a 
 regular Friends of Trees planting on Saturday\, January 29th (8:15am - 1:00
 pm). \n\nThe classroom session will be held at Kaiser Town Hall at 3704 N. 
 Interstate in Portland.\n\nYou need to be able to attend both sessions in o
 rder to become an Assistant Crew Leader.\n\nPlease contact Andy Meeks at 50
 3-282-8846\, ext. 24 or AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org for more information.
