DESCRIPTION:We are delighted to planting in Oregon City this spring! Join u
 s in planting over 20 new trees around the Eastham School property to celeb
 rate Arbor Day! \n\nPlease arrive around 12:45pm to be registered and assig
 ned to a crew. The planting will start promptly at 1:00pm. We provide snack
 s and drinking water\, as well as gloves\, tools and guidance. Please come 
 dressed for the weather\, wear sturdy shoes\, and get ready to have fun! \n
 \nIndividual RSVPs are not required\, however for groups of 5 or more\, ple
 ase contact Jenny or Randi at (503) 595-0213. Feel free to call if you have
  any questions or need more information. We look forward to seeing you ther
 e!
