DESCRIPTION:Please arrive to the staging site\, the Dharma Zen Rain Center\
 , by 8:45am to enjoy some hot coffee and breakfast treats.  The planting st
 arts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves and tools\, so all you need to d
 o is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes.  Our neighbo
 rhood volunteers will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers after
  the planting is complete. \n\n<b>This event will have people planting tree
 s by bike! Want to join the bike team?</b> Sign up <a href=http://friendsof
 trees.org/volunteering/how-can-you-help/plant-trees-by-bike>HERE.</a> Biker
 s with trailers and cargo bikes are awesome and everyone with a bike is wel
 come to take part of our bike planting efforts.\n\n<b>Looking to volunteer 
 as a group?</b> Due to popular interest\, this planting is now FULL and clo
 sed to additional groups. We encourage groups to consider our other plantin
 gs happening this same day/time in SW Portland and NE Vancouver\, WA. \n\nP
 lease contact Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have questions or need any fur
 ther information.\n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!\n\n<b>Thank y
 ou to Dragonfly Coffee House for generously sponsoring this event!<b>\n\n
