DESCRIPTION:Please join us for our annual Fruit Tree Giveaway and Shade Tre
 es sale held here at the Friends of Trees office.  We won't know the exact 
 stock we'll have available until a few days prior to this event but there w
 ill very likely be dwarf and semi-dwarf varieties of apples\, plums\, and p
 ears -- and potentially other options as well.  We'll also be clearing out 
 the remainder of our unsold 8-12' street tree stock from this season and se
 lling them at wholesale prices.  \n\nFor more information\, please contact 
 Andrew at andrewl@friendsoftrees.org or 503-467-2518.  We'd love to see you
  there!
