UID:5svdluc9vscqiblm7jp9hia0ld@google.com
CREATED:20230829T131403Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b>===========</b></p><p><b>Due to projected inclement weath
 er\, <u>this event is postponed until Sat\, Jan 27th</u>.  </b>Thank you fo
 r your understanding -- we very much hope to plant with you on the 27th!</p
 ><p><b>===========</b></p><p><b>Let's plant trees together in Vancouver! </
 b>Interested in receiving a tree? Click <a href="https://friendsoftrees.org
 /get-a-tree/"><u><u><b><u>HERE</u></b></u></u></a> to purchase a tree for y
 our household. Dozens of large (6-10' tall) trees will be ready for plantin
 g in their new homes\, and your help is what makes this community planting 
 possible!</p><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planti
 ng crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and gui
 dance\, as well as light breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate. We 
 ask that all volunteers dress for the weather\, wear sturdy shoes/boots you
  don't mind getting dirty\, and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Have a picku
 p truck?</b> We need your help getting these young trees to their planting 
 sites a few blocks away from the central staging site. <b><a href="https://
 www.tfaforms.com/4840511?tfa_26=a0T5G00000fQk9I&tfa_2189=Central-East%20Van
 couver%20neighborhood%20planting&tfa_31=a0V5G00000W2cif&tfa_45=Truck%20Driv
 er\,%20%20at%20January%2013\,%202024%20at%208:30%20am&tfa_2190=2024-01-13&t
 fa_49=4.5&tfa_886=Standard%20FOT&tfa_51=offsite"><u><u>Please sign up</u></
 u></a></b> if you're able to help out in this key role. </p><p><b>Want to p
 lant by bike?</b> This event will have a <b><a href="https://friendsoftrees
 .org/volunteer/how-to-volunteer/bike-planter/"><u>bike-powered crew</u></a>
 </b>. Bring your bike\, helmet\, and a bike trailer (if you have one)\, <b>
 <a href="https://www.tfaforms.com/4840511?tfa_26=a0T5G00000fQk9I&tfa_2189=C
 entral-East%20Vancouver%20neighborhood%20planting&tfa_31=a0VPa000000b7Ab&tf
 a_45=%20Bike%20Planter%20at%20January%2013\,%202024%20at%208:45%20am&tfa_21
 90=2024-01-13&tfa_49=4.25&tfa_886=Standard%20FOT&tfa_51=offsite"><u>sign-up
  here</u></a></b>.</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request that youth 15 and 
 under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer o
 n their own and will need to hand us a <a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/y
 outhwaiver"><u><u><b><u>youth waiver form</u></b></u></u></a> signed by the
 ir parent/guardian.</p><p><b>Private transportation</b>: You will travel fr
 om the meeting location to a few planting sites in the nearby neighborhood 
 (up to several miles). <b>We recommend private transportation</b> (bike or 
 vehicle)\, but there may be an option to carpool if others in your small pl
 anting crew are also comfortable with this. </p><p><b>Where will these tree
 s be planted? </b>In the following neighborhoods: <span>Burton Ridge\, </sp
 an><span>DuBois Park\, </span><span>Ellsworth Springs\, </span><span>Evergr
 een Highlands\, </span><span>Father Blanchet Park\, </span><span>Forest Rid
 ge\, </span><span>Marrion\, </span><span>North Garrison Heights\, </span><s
 pan>Northcrest\, </span><span>Northwood\, </span><span>Oakbrook\, </span><s
 pan>Old Evergreen Hwy\, and </span><span>Vancouver Heights.</span></p><p><b
 >Questions?  </b>Please check out our <a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/v
 olunteer-faq/"><u><u><u><u><b><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></b></u></u></u><
 /u></a>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  Reach us at <a href="mailto:Vo
 lunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org<
 /u></b></u></u></u></u></a> We look forward to planting together soon!<br><
 /p><p></p><hr /><p></p><p>This event is in partnership with the City of Van
 couver.</p>
