 nd click 'Get Started.' Be sure you answer the questions at "get started" b
 y 10/31/2011. \n\nPlease arrive by 8:45am and we'll provide coffee and doug
 hnuts to get your started.  We'll also provide gloves and tools\, so all yo
 u need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes!  
 The neighborhood group will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers
  after the planting in complete.\n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there
 !
