CREATED:20190808T153327Z
DESCRIPTION:Neighbors will plant trees in their neighborhood. Click on &quo
 t\;Order Street &amp\; Yard Trees&quot\; to set up an account to buy trees 
 for your yard or parking strip.\n\nOnce you set up an account\, Friends of 
 Trees will arrange for the city of Portland to inspect the planting site an
 d issue a permit. For this planting\, you must create your account by Jan 5
  and order your trees by Feb 16.\n\nQuestions? Contact your Neighborhood Co
 ordinator.\n\nBeaumont-Wilshire: Camryn\, 503-255-0992 or cporkandi@yahoo.c
 om.\n\nCully: Starr\, 503-282-2973 or cullytrees@comcast.net.\n\nMadison So
 uth: Jillian\, 503-989-8115 or jillianmarie_m@yahoo.com.\n\nRose City Park:
