 ghnuts to get your started. We'll also provide gloves and tools\, so all yo
 u need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes. T
 he neighborhood group will also provide a potluck lunch for all volunteers 
 after the planting in complete. This planting is generously sponsored by Po
 rtland General Electric.\n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!  RSVPs
  are not required.  Please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org o
 r (503) 595-0213 for more information.
